  "remarks": "\nSTANEX GROUP LIMITED LIABILITY PARTNERSHIP is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the following ground: STANEX GROUP LIMITED LIABILITY PARTNERSHIP is associated with KAZSTANEX LLP and UZSTANEX LLC by receiving a material benefit from KAZSTANEX and UZSTANEX. KAZSTANEX and UZSTANEX are involved persons as defined in the regulations.   \n",
